\title{category with representable maps}
\date{2023-03-05T11:54:04+01:00}
\taxon{definition}
\author{jonmsterling}

\import{base-macros}
\def\Repr[arg1]{\mathrm{R}_{\arg1}}


\p{A \em{category with representable maps} or \em{CwR} is defined by [Uemura](uemura-2021-thesis) to be a category #{\mathcal{C}} with finite limits equipped with a pullback-stable class #{\Repr{\mathcal{C}}\subseteq \Homs{\mathcal{C}}} of [exponentiable arrows](jms-0031) in #{\mathcal{C}}.}